{"Title": "Towards a regional science academy: A manifesto", "Year": 2016, "Source": "Reg.", "Volume": "3", "Issue": 1, "Art.No": null, "PageStart": null, "PageEnd": null, "CitedBy": 2, "DOI": "10.18335/region.v3i1.120", "Link": "https://www.scopus.com/inward/record.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&scp=85006155223&origin=inward", "Abstract": "\u00a9 2016, European Regional Science Association. All rights reserved.This Manifesto provides a joint proposal to create a Regional Science Academy as a think-tank support platform for a strategic development of the spatial sciences. The Regional Science Academy is a strategic spatial knowledge catalyst: it acts as a global intellectual powerhouse for new knowledge network initiatives and scholarly views on regions and cities as vital centrepieces of interconnected spatial systems. This contribution highlights its role and presents various activity plans.", "AuthorKeywords": null, "IndexKeywords": null, "DocumentType": "Journal", "PublicationStage": null, "OpenAccess": 1, "EID": "2-s2.0-85006155223", "SubjectAreas": [["Geography, Planning and Development", "SOCI", "3305"], ["Economics and Econometrics", "ECON", "2002"]], "AuthorData": {"7102958684": {"Name": "Nijkamp P.", "AuthorID": "7102958684", "AffiliationID": "60008734", "AffiliationName": "Free University of Amsterdam"}, "25930439500": {"Name": "Kourtit K.", "AuthorID": "25930439500", "AffiliationID": "60002014", "AffiliationName": "KTH Royal Institute of Technology"}, "55757057000": {"Name": "Khattabi A.", "AuthorID": "55757057000", "AffiliationID": null, "AffiliationName": null}, "7201500066": {"Name": "Rose A.", "AuthorID": "7201500066", "AffiliationID": null, "AffiliationName": null}, "14622816400": {"Name": "Kocornik-Mina A.", "AuthorID": "14622816400", "AffiliationID": null, "AffiliationName": null}, "14017644600": {"Name": "Faggian A.", "AuthorID": "14017644600", "AffiliationID": null, "AffiliationName": null}, "7403271479": {"Name": "Scott A.", "AuthorID": "7403271479", "